parameters:
This doesn't seem like the student council room,
does it?

Moreover, this scenery doesn't seem like it's
inside the academy.

But, this place is still inside the Caledonia
Magic Academy, you know.

I wonder if this is a magically created space.
Considering it's a school with a long history, it
wouldn't be strange to have something like this.

(The magic research club room and all... What an
extraordinary school.)

(There must be a reason why this academy has
produced so many famous wizards.)

MasamuneIt seems like there's a barrier
preventing us from entering. Could this rock be
the cause?

MasamuneI don't have any magic to break the
rock. Is there any other way?

DogI'm thirsty. I won't move until I drink
water.
MasamuneI'll be in trouble if you don't move.

DogI'm thirsty. I won't move until I drink
water.

MasamuneWhy is there a dog in a place like
this, to begin with?

Magical DollThis is the Cleonta Defense Layer.
Unauthorized individuals are not allowed to enter
the Student Council Room.

Magical DollHowever, those who have the
qualifications can pass. If you can bring three
oranges, I will let you through.

Magical DollOh, it seems you have brought
them.

Magical DollNow, this is the final trial. If
you can defeat this familiar, I will grant you the
right to enter the Student Council Room.

Magical DollCongratulations. I will eat the
oranges.

MasamuneDoes this book have a will? Well,
whatever. I'll let it be read.

MasamuneRock breaking magic, huh? It's a good
magic.

Flying GrimoireIn exchange for learning magic,
you have to pay a price.

Flying GrimoireThe price is to shout the name
of the person you've fantasized about the most
during masturbation.

AmeliaMasturbation... might be a little
intriguing.

Masamune(There's no way I can say something so
embarrassing...)

MasamuneI had no choice... There were no other
girls around.

AmeliaCertainly, that's true... but I never
expected to become the subject of someone's
masturbation fantasies.

AmeliaNo, it's fine. In fact, it's making my
heart race.

Masamune There seems to be a well here. We can
draw water from it.

Masamune We should draw water from it just in
case we need it.

Amelia Hmm... I can sense a little bit of
magical power.
Amelia Just in case, I'll draw the water.
Masamune Ah... But is it okay?
Amelia Leave it to me, big sister.
Masamune So there was a trap after all.
Amelia No... I can't negate it.

Mysterious Voice If you listen to my
instructions, the curse will be lifted. First,
please take off all of your clothes.

Amelia Impossible... It's quite powerful...
Mmm, I never thought this magic would be so
ineffective.

Amelia My magical power is being drained
rapidly...

Amelia Well, it seems like we have no choice
but to listen.

Masamune (I guess... there's no other choice...
and it's still better than having anyone else
here)
Amelia This won't do, will it?

Amelia Isn't this too much...? Normally, you
would avert your eyes, right?

Masamune (The current Amelia isn't the same
person anymore, huh)
Amelia I mean, you're getting an erection...

Amelia You're definitely planning to masturbate
later, aren't you?

Masamune (Amelia... You never used to make
dirty jokes like this...)

Mysterious Voice Then, please answer with the
most exciting masturbation fantasy you've ever
had.

Amelia I have to say it or else it won't be
unlocked... hmm...

Amelia Um... I got the most excited by
fantasizing about having sex with Masamune...
Amelia Wow, this is so embarrassing...
Masamune (Is it me... I'm so happy)

Amelia But it can't be helped... I get horny
sometimes too, you know.

Mysterious Voice A lie has been detected. The
curse will not be lifted.
Amelia U-Um, is that... a lie?

Mysterious Voice Please tell me the fantasy
that made you the most excited during
masturbation.
Masamune (So, it means it's not me...)
Amelia This is... just a fantasy.

Amelia What excites me the most... is
fantasizing about being forcefully violated by my
senpai.

Amelia What excited me the most was being
forcefully creampied by a big dick.
Mysterious Voice ...The curse will be lifted.

Amelia Phew... I'm glad. With this, we were
able to safely obtain the water.
Amelia Did you get disgusted after all?

Masamune It's okay... I also have strange
fantasies sometimes.

Magical DollWe magical dolls were created to
protect the student council room in this defense
recollection.
Magical DollI will... allow you to pass.

Magical DollThe strength of a magical doll is
determined by its master. Our master, Moonchild-
sama, is very strong, so I am also strong. Ehehe.
HP and MP have been fully restored!
HP and MP have been fully restored!
